title.rendered: STEDI SQUARE TYPE PUSH SWITCHES TO SUIT STEDI FASCIA PANELS

content.rendered:
Toyota Square Push Switch OEM Style

DETAILS

Square 22 x 22mm Push latching type switch designed for the range of STEDI switch fascia panels.

KEY FEATURES

  • Ice Blue LED Back Lighting
  • Green Upper Light is Active when Power is ON
  • Lower Light is Active when Dash Lights are ON
  • Laser Etched print ensure our print will never rub off with use
  • Rated at 3A on 12v

COMPATIBLE FASCIA PANELS

  • STEDI 70 Series Panel
  • STEDI Ford Everest, Raptor & Ranger Panel

Please ensure a our switches are always wired through a fused relay.

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Ice Blue Lower and Green Upper
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 22 x 22mm
RATED 3A @ 12v

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1 x Toyota Push Button Switch
  • 1 x Green Connector with Wire Tails
  • Wiring Diagram
